"* OPEN (2026-07-07): the `catch:` family runs its protected block via
"* execute_block; a self-nesting protected block compounds Rust frames per level
"* and SIGBUSes uncatchably (exit 138). Same fix as each_reenter.qn: the
"* execute_block stack-watermark check.

var f = nil;
f = { { f.value }.catch:{ |e| e.throw } };
f.value;
'unreachable'.print
